{"tid":2104522,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"男士毛孔大+多， 有咩洗面產品可以推介","createTime":"2020-07-12T04:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T08:44:20.000Z","uid":250073,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13a77545517b1cef605641e5138871215ecca268","tid":2104522,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n搞到塊面望落去同摸落去都一啲都唔滑， 好「鞋」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打有親身用過覺得好嘅產品推介"},{"pid":"1c92fdcae045a14d45172351f7e3b1b45a53ce7f","tid":2104522,"uid":132322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13a77545517b1cef605641e5138871215ecca268","tid":2104522,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n搞到塊面望落去同摸落去都一啲都唔滑， 好「鞋」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打有親身用過覺得好嘅產品推介"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"毛孔收唔到架<br />\n鞋手可能係角質層，買Ｄ去角質面膜(果酸類/泥mask)一個星期用一次"},{"pid":"3e6db34fce57f0255cf8f52a2a0bf795a0dbd29a","tid":2104522,"uid":48711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"係咪可以用激光打死毛孔裏面既細胞等佢唔出油 咁個毛孔就會細d？"},{"pid":"f31332be51a009e909337ae18623ee2a224a1d3d","tid":2104522,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n多毛孔黑頭點搞<br />\n<br />\n同埋好似粒粒野生完之後留疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到好核凸<br />\n我暗倉唔係生得出  但唔知點解周不時會有D細肉粒窿起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以令到自己塊面光滑D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2564b01705796610b1ab17bb2e13f55794709ccd","tid":2104522,"uid":288107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"毛孔：去美容院做微針／激光微針／其他激光類美容先會收到毛孔，其他方法唔洗諗，唔會太work<br />\n<br />\n如果皮膚鞋：可以用簡稱AHA類嘅酸性化學去角質，例如glycolic acid、lactic acid<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/alpha_hydroxy_acids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSkincareAddiction%2Fwiki%2Falpha_hydroxy_acids&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNniwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=0bda2910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/alpha_hydroxy_acids</a><br />\n<br />\n如果黑頭多：可以用簡稱BHA類嘅酸性化學去角質，例如salycilic acid，或者含2% salycilic acid 嘅洗面檢液，更高䃈可以試呢個方法，好多人話work：<a href=\"https://fiftyshadesofsnail.com/2015/03/28/how-to-shrink-pores-temporarily-plus-3-pore-myths/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiftyshadesofsnail.com%2F2015%2F03%2F28%2Fhow-to-shrink-pores-temporarily-plus-3-pore-myths%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNniwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=f0839f1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fiftyshadesofsnail.com/2015/03/28/how-to-shrink-pores-temporarily-plus-3-pore-myths/</a> <br />\n<br />\nBHA: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/beta_hydroxy_acids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSkincareAddiction%2Fwiki%2Fbeta_hydroxy_acids&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNniwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=20ed39e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/beta_hydroxy_acids</a> <br />\n<br />\n以上都要由低劑量用起，每星期兩三次就夠，最好連同正確洗面同保濕步驟做。<br />\n<br />\n個人推介the ordinary呢個牌子，因為香港有專門店，一d其他店舖都有賣，因為價錢真係好平（50-70蚊支）和唔會賣廣告同唔會成日出新產品賣d唔等駛野。其實皮膚產品來去幾十年都係個d基礎成份，唔洗比好多錢買。貴個d都係買牌子同廣告同埋每季整d濕9新產品博你買。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/routine_order#wiki_actives\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSkincareAddiction%2Fwiki%2Froutine_order%23wiki_actives&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNniwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=083036f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/SkincareAddiction/wiki/routine_order#wiki_actives</a>"},{"pid":"65a16c8d4134a05fe961c33fcd100c99612d088d","tid":2104522,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"有啲錢就睇皮膚科醫生啦<br />\n美容院信唔過"},{"pid":"3cb4224959bd6eb61e31acabb7327c1b0a03c9cf","tid":2104522,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a16c8d4134a05fe961c33fcd100c99612d088d","tid":2104522,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"有啲錢就睇皮膚科醫生啦<br />\n美容院信唔過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"都好wo<br />\n想問下因為我依家唔係爛面濕疹果種大問題，只係想扮靚皮膚好d, 醫生都有藥開？ <br />\n因為感覺上睇皮膚科醫生係要去到好大問題先需要，美容問題覺得係去返美容<br />\n<br />\n利申： 0 美容知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea452ef09af11671df84f7fde0df56830d8e177","tid":2104522,"uid":141237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"試下用Dr.G<br />\n<br />\n新手啱用，佢有齊晒一set（果支唔記得係咩水，洗面奶，同埋一支搽面乳液）<br />\n<br />\n而且價錢好便，大概1set先$300-400。<br />\n可以用1個月半。<br />\n<br />\n個人經驗，用洗面奶洗面既時候用「手指既力」輕輕微打圈去柔塊面，同一個位唔好柔超過10次左右，唔係就傷，同埋唔好太快，太快又係會刷傷。即使你feel到有d位都係凸凸地，唔好搞佢。<br />\n<br />\n其次，唔好抱太大幻想，你抱既期望往往永遠都係高於產品帶黎既作用好多好多，你做完晒成個護膚過程，就完，唔好左照右照，係咁係度摸點解d毛孔咁黑咁大㗎，我地始終無研究開皮膚既嘢，你永遠唔會清楚毛孔真正狀況係點，好似你見到毛孔有d凸出黎類似粉刺既嘢，好有可能佢係之前傷左，依家埋緊口所以凸左出黎，而你又走去R損佢，咁你d皮膚就一直都係有問題。<br />\n<br />\n毛孔洗完有d都係黑黑地，有可能只係毛孔本身其它問題，而唔係清潔唔乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n我地男仔最大護膚問題，就係我地誤解左真正護膚完之後個樣究竟係點，我地成日以為護膚要做得啱，出到黎個樣應該係韓劇入面d男主角咁先叫做得啱，其實唔係㗎，只要你唔好成日搞佢，佢油既時候去洗洗塊面，乾就搽保濕，訓前做好個洗面保濕steps，自然你d皮膚就好乾淨，雖然毛孔會唔會收細就唔知，但係起碼會乾淨好多唔會惡化落去先。"},{"pid":"f48e40b66ffe657b2fdca587ec085dfdbc6b3004","tid":2104522,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"美容院針清"},{"pid":"06551b91e320b356557e6c5595a09673dcb7b8ab","tid":2104522,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:33:41.000Z","msg":"斯巴"},{"pid":"4b58591236e194d57b228d1240904e102423c543","tid":2104522,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"去美容鋪啦 一個月一次 一次先3-400<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}